metadata.name: Turtle Slide
metadata.description:
Girl surfing a turtle  
Piece #1  
NFT 4 STF is a collection of 6 unique illustrations that are all inspired by the ocean, the love for surfing and powerful women. The 1st holder of each NFT will receive a physical print of their new artwork. 40% of primary sales will be donated to the Sea Turtles Forever non-profit.
